Story :

A story about love, volleyball, and competition of Sand (Jittakorn Bhunsorn), an ordinary guy who&#039;s the leader of a gang in Pattaya beach and Net (Sara Malagul Len), a pretty girl who&#039;s a prosperous beach volleyball player. Sand falls for Net and tries to win her heart while Net is attracted by Peat (Siwas Naroupai), her young coach whom she adores as her hero. When a big volleyball match is coming, Net has to face her terrific rivals like Rayko (Russamee Thongsiripraisri ), a half Japanese-Thai beach volleyball champion. This big match is a twist of Net&#039;s life and is a big attempt for Sand to prove his true love.
